OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781017874
OL,3,CFour men in hospital after serious
OL,4,Ccollision in police chase
OL,6,FA serious collision following a police
OL,7,Fchase north of Hastings has left four
OL,8,Fpeople in hospital.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to reports of a
OL,11,Fsuspected gunshot and disturbance in
OL,12,FSidley Green at around 11.50pm on
OL,13,FMonday night (8 June).
OL,15,FArmed officers and a police dog unit
OL,16,Fattended the area, with no injuries
OL,17,Freported from the suspect gunshot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
