OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781017874
OL,3,CFour men in hospital after serious
OL,4,Ccollision in police chase
OL,6,FThe three passengers, a 21-year-old
OL,7,Fman from Bexhill, a 23-year-old man
OL,8,Ffrom Bexhill and a 36-year-old man
OL,9,Ffrom St Leonards, were arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of affray.
OL,12,FAll four men remain in hospital where
OL,13,Fthey are under police guard.
OL,15,FEnquiries remain ongoing to establish
OL,16,Fthe circumstances of the disturbance
OL,17,Fand suspected gunshot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
