OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781017874
OL,3,CFour men in hospital after serious
OL,4,Ccollision in police chase
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Jay Mendis-
OL,7,FGunasekera said: "This is a fast-
OL,8,Fmoving investigation and we are
OL,9,Fworking hard to establish the full
OL,10,Fcircumstances of both incidents.
OL,12,F"We understand the concern this will
OL,13,Fcause within the community and there
OL,14,Fwill be an increased police presence
OL,15,Fin the area while enquiries continue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
